we have to add this Service to Manifest using Android Studio Editor Get Here - https://qwertycube.com/apk-editor-studio/download/
Then we able to register app in Special Notification Access Permission.

<service android:name="YOUR_PACKAGE_NAME_HERE"
            android:label="NotificationAlertAccess"
          	 android:permission="android.permission.BIND_NOTIFICATION_LISTENER_SERVICE">
      	 <intent-filter>
            <action android:name="android.service.notification.NotificationListenerService" />
       	 </intent-filter>
</service>
